###
### Volume
###

# Increase Volume
"pamixer --increase 5"
	XF86AudioRaiseVolume

# Decrease Volume
"pamixer --decrease 5"
	XF86AudioLowerVolume

# Mute Audio
"pamixer --toggle-mute"
	XF86AudioMute

###
### Backlight
###

# Increase Brightness
"light -A 5"
	XF86MonBrightnessUp

# Decrease Brightness
"light -U 5"
	XF86MonBrightnessDown
